Hello,
I am uploading code to the robot, but the code doesn’t work. After turning the robot off and on again, the same code starts working. Randomly – sometimes it works, sometimes it doesn’t. When we try to run simple codes, there is no issue, but more complex code structures seem to be problematic. Do you have any insights into the possible source of this problem? Thank you in advance for your assistance.

At least, not without seeing your code, knowing what issues you’re seeing (including specifics like error messages or log files), and knowing what your robot looks like (i.e. what mechanism is controlled by what motor with what gearbox ratio, etc)
